lass=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 27, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ryl1665702781725.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ryl1665702781725.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ryl1665702781725.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ryl1665702781725\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ryl1665702781725___asin_252891\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the arc sine of X.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__topic_d80474e1_d80475e1_d80476e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__p_d80477e1_d80478e1_d80479e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$asin</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__section_w2961ab1b7b5_w2962ab1b7_w2963ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__p_d80480e1_d80481e1_d80482e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vResult = $asin(1 / 2)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__topic_d52977e1_d52978e1_d52979e1_d52980e1_d52981e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641945e83\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__d6803e20\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>—numeric value in the range -1 through 1, inclusive.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__topic_d52982e1_d52983e1_d52984e1_d52985e1_d52986e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641945e95\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__p_d80492e1_d80493e1_d80494e1\">Calculated arc sine value.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__p_d80495e1_d80496e1_d80497e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__table_d8009e1_d8010e1_d8011e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following this\n            Function</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__table_d8009e1_d8010e1_d8011e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__table_d8009e1_d8010e1_d8011e1__entry__2\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__table_d8009e1_d8010e1_d8011e1__entry__3\">`</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryl1665702781725__table_d8009e1_d8010e1_d8011e1__entry__1\"> -1203 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryl1665702781725__table_d8009e1_d8010e1_d8011e1__entry__2\"> &lt;UPROCERR_RANGE&gt; </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryl1665702781725__table_d8009e1_d8010e1_d8011e1__entry__3\"> Value out of range. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__topic_d52987e1_d52988e1_d52989e1_d52990e1_d52991e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641945e159\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__topic_d52992e1_d52993e1_d52994e1_d52995e1_d52996e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641945e168\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryl1665702781725__p_d80507e1_d80508e1_d80509e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$asin</span> calculates the arc sine of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>, that is, it returns that angle, in radians, whose sine (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$sin</span>) is <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example returns the arc sine of the given expression:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vResult = $asin(1 / 2)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fri1719653551559.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$sin</a><p>Return the sine of X.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$asin Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 27, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the arc sine of X. $asin ( X ) Example: vResult = $asin(1 / 2) Parameters X —numeric value in the range -1 through 1, inclusive. Return Values Calculated arc sine value. If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 1. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following this Function Value Error constant ` -1203 <UPROCERR_RANGE> Value out of range. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The function $asin calculates the arc sine of X , that is, it returns that angle, in radians, whose sine ( $sin ) is X . The following example returns the arc sine of the given expression: vResult = $asin(1 / 2) Copy Related Links $sin Return the sine of X. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}